directory: .
domain: Root of the CTX workspace — an opinionated agentic coding system providing (1) a strict Rust lint regime shared with template/, (2) a context-tree pipeline (.context/ ctx/rollup.ctx generation, scan, access-gating) that forces top-down reading before edits, and (3) a deferred architecture-audit layer whose prompt/hook scaffolding already exists. Depending on the root means getting the dogfooded lint config, the six ctx-* crates, and the docs/prompts that define their contracts.
edit_notes:
  - Root Cargo.toml, clippy.toml, deny.toml, rust-toolch